        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>The QA team will perform functional, UI, and validation checks on the Liability Information screen. <br/>
All fields, controls, and behaviors must match the specifications outlined in the provided requirements table. Any deviations, defects, or usability issues must be documented.</p>

<p><b>Verify the Action Values Scenarios in the Logic tab from the below Excel sheet</b><br/>
<a href="https://zurichinsurancecan.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/sites/FMZTCSpreSOWspace/Shared%20Documents/General/IPS_CIIM_ezDocs%20Integration/IPS%20Integration%20-%20Master%20Sheets/Received%20Liability%20Master.xlsx?d=wde7fd63e6c4d446481a48860e88c373e&amp;csf=1&amp;web=1&amp;e=RTJxAx" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><ins>Received Liability Master.xlsx</ins></a></p>

