        <tr id="comment-body-1619363"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p>I have completed testing the QA - IPSIntegration - Validate Received Liability Information Screen - Logic - AdditionalInsured. All fields are functioning as expected.</p>

<p>Therefore, I am proceeding to close the story.</p>

<p>Please refer to the attached documents for reference.</p>

